snippet.title: Monogolf - Trailer
snippet.description:
Monogolf has only one rule: Reach the hole in one shot.

• Play Monogolf to make a long journey feel shorter. 

• Tryhard while waiting for that friend who is always late.

• Craft mini golf holes with the Level Editor when you are chilling at home.

• Wait for the bus while giving your best on Challenge Mode. 

Whatever it is you are doing, Monogolf is always the mini golf game you want by your side.

FEATURES:

• Arcade mode with 150 mini golf holes. Every 10 of them you will discover new obstacles to overcome. 

• Challenge mode! Each challenge you beat gives you a new skin for your ball.

• Complete Level Editor. Share your creations with us via Twitter, Discord and Instagram.

Have fun!
